{
  "texts": [
    "CaiTI logs the user response if CaiTI still fails to classify the rephrased Segment into the format of (Dimension, Score).",
    "Otherwise, CaiTI checks the Score no matter if thisSegment is answering the question asked by CaiTI or not.",
    "If the user needs more attention in this dimension (Score = 2), CaiTI proceeds with a reflection-validation (R-V) process starting with asking for more information starting with a simple reflection in MI.",
    "An example of this process is presented in Figure 5.The R-V process is described in detail in Section 5.",
    "At the end, CaiTI generates a report that follows the same format as the therapists' notes during their treatment sessions."
  ]
}